# Grok-4-Fast Model Context Settings

model: x-ai/grok-4-fast

description: |
  Configure Cursor to use the Grok 4 Fast model from xAI.
  This model supports a total context window of **2,000,000 tokens** and allows up to **30,000 output tokens**.
  Prevent unnecessary post-task noise by disabling the automatic generation of excessive summary or log documents.

rules:

- name: grok-4-fast-token-limits
    applyTo: all
    config:
      max_input_tokens: 2000000
      max_output_tokens: 30000

- name: disable-excessive-summaries
    description: Prevent creation of unnecessary summary documents after task completion.
    applyTo: all
    config:
      generate_summaries: false
      post_task_summaries: disabled
      cleanup_behavior: minimal
